content.value: 13 TV's throughout!
Never miss your game.
NFL, SEC, Big 10
And more...
Live Music
Every Weekend!
Welcome to Flashback - Richmond Hill's Heartbeat of Rock 'n' Roll!

Nestled in the vibrant heart of Richmond Hill, GA, Flashback stands as a beloved family-owned gem, passionately run by Jimmy and Laura Castiglione. As THE Coastal Empire’s premier rock venue, we're more than just a bar; we're a celebration of the golden era of rock.

Our journey began with a dream to create a place where the electrifying energy of the 60s, 70s, and 80s rock lives on. Today, Flashback is not just a venue; it’s a cultural haven for music enthusiasts of all ages. Here, every corner echoes with the legends of rock, and every night is an ode to the music that defined generations.

At Flashback, we offer a full menu brimming with mouth-watering delights and daily dinner specials that cater to every palate. Our 13 strategically placed TVs ensure you won't miss a beat of college and NFL games, with coverage including the SEC, Big 10, and the NFL ticket.

But that's not all! Every Friday and Saturday night, our stage lights up with live music, showcasing local talents and keeping the spirit of rock alive. For those who enjoy a bit of friendly competition, our pool tables and dart boards are ready for your best shot.

Flashback is more than just a bar; it's a community. We welcome all ages to join our party, where the vibe is always high, and the food and drink specials never disappoint. It's a place where memories are made, friendships are forged, and the spirit of rock 'n' roll thrives.
So, come on over to Flashback, where every visit is a throwback to the best times of rock and the promise of a great time. Let's make some memories together!
with Poker & Karaoke
Kick your Wednesdays up a notch at Flashback with our unbeatable

Fly Like An Eagle wings. The fun doesn't stop there—starting at 7pm, grab the spotlight with karaoke or ante up for poker night. It's your midweek pick-me-up with tasty wings, tunes, and cards, all under one roof.
with Live Acoustic Music
$10 Burger Baskets

Join us every Thursday for our $10 burger baskets.  A hearty burger with your choice of hand-cut chips, fries, crispy tater tots, onion rings and more.  It's your weekly backstage pass to the best eats in town, served with a side of chill vibes and cold drinks.  So, call up your crew, snag a table, and come dive into a deal that hits all the right notes.
Trivia with a Twist and Tacos

Spice up your week with Taco Tuesday at Flashback, where delicious tacos meet brain-busting trivia starting at 7pm. Dive into our mouth-watering selection of tacos, crafted with the freshest ingredients and a dash of culinary creativity, perfect for fueling your trivia conquests.

But the fun doesn't stop at tacos! Quench your thirst and amp up the excitement with our Domestic Beer Bucket Specials. Grab your friends and enjoy 6 cold ones for just $21, the ideal complement to your taco feast and trivia feats.
